If i make a easy example of this, ok get into character - you are queing up in a fast food outlet.. the que has a few people in it and you've been waiting a while. Then some Big guy from a behind the line walks up past the que pushes you out of the way takeing your spot.. you were going to be the next served customer.... what do you do? <br>
<br>
You cant push the guy behind him so you walk to the back of the que - sometimes the guy behind the one who just pushed in forfeit's there line and lets you slip in first... at this point the guy behind him either whines.. if he doesnt it's normally ok (gah cant please everyone)<br>
